# Elevate Apparel Brand Theme

Follow the full theme spec in [CLAUDE.md](../../CLAUDE.md) (**Elevate Apparel Brand Theme**). Every page must match this system.

## Fonts

- UI: Geist Sans (`font-sans`)
- Editorial only: Playfair Display (`font-serif`)
- Mono rare: Geist Mono (`font-mono`)
- Do not introduce Inter/Roboto/system as the brand face

## Colors (match live UI)

- Backgrounds: `#0a0a0b`, `#090909`, `#111110`, `#1a1815`, `black`
- Gold: `#e3bb78`, `#e0bd7d`, CTA `#e5bd79` / `#e5bd78`, hover `#eec98a`
- Text: white / `#f4f4f5`; muted `#b5b0a8`; on-gold `#18120b`
- Borders: `#2d2a27`, `#37332c`, `#292929`
- CSS tokens also in `frontend/app/globals.css` (`--color-gold`, `--color-surface*`)

## UI patterns

- Max width `1400px`
- Sharp radii (`rounded-[4px]`–`rounded-lg`), not pill-heavy
- Uppercase compact gold CTAs; gold focus rings
- Dark-first; no purple/indigo glow themes; no cream broadsheet defaults

When building or restyling any page, reuse header/footer/auth/homepage visual language.
